video.synopsis: Teenage spy McKeyla teams up with three other super-smart girls to become secret agents who use their science and tech skills to save the day.

episodes.synopsis: New girl and teen spy McKeyla stirs up suspicions in classmates Adrienne, Bryden and Camryn, causing them to do some investigative work of their own.
episodes.title: The New Girl

episodes.synopsis: McKeyla investigates a threat to the prince's space mission while Adrienne, Bryden and Camryn stumble through proving their spy skills.
episodes.title: Secret Agenting

episodes.synopsis: The girls band together in science and friendship. Will they be able to save the prince's space launch in time and become official NOV8 agents?
episodes.title: Smart is the New Cool

episodes.synopsis: The Quail sends the girls back to school with orders to keep their spy status a secret. But it's not long before a mysterious new threat appears.
episodes.title: Back to Basics

episodes.synopsis: As Retro wreaks havoc on Maywood Glen's technology, the girls get themselves sent to detention to dig up more info on their main suspect.
episodes.title: No Laughing Matter

episodes.synopsis: When a new piece of evidence involving HAVOC points to Carson Lazarus, Adrienne and Bryden comb through her trash looking for clues.
episodes.title: Trashed

episodes.synopsis: Bryden's voice analysis gives the girls a new theory about Retro's identity, but it'll take extra smarts to keep up their spying during a blackout.
episodes.title: Dam Fine Mess

episodes.synopsis: Retro sets a trap for the girls that leaves NOV8 open to attack, and the Quail tells McKeyla they need to leave town for their own safety.
episodes.title: Bye Bye Birdie

episodes.synopsis: When the girls learn about the Quail and McKeyla's super-secret plan to infiltrate HAVOC, they enlist some new friends to help out with the mission.
episodes.title: Mission Totally Possible

episodes.synopsis: The Falcon tasks the girls with investigating a string of robberies, and EDM band EliTe returns to Maywood Glen to perform a surprise concert.
episodes.title: Finding Maddy

episodes.synopsis: While Bry and Cam do some sleuthing at rehearsal, Adri and Ember create a gummy bear tracking device to help McKeyla find Maddy.
episodes.title: Gummying Up The Works

episodes.synopsis: When a nightmare about Maddy leaves her reeling, McKeyla comes clean to the Falcon. Bry and Cam kill it at auditions -- and zero in on a new suspect.
episodes.title: Crate Expectations

episodes.synopsis: Ember's itching potion sends Grady to the nurse's office, where Adri and McKeyla question him. Bry discovers a mysterious clue in EliTe's music.
episodes.title: One Track Mind

episodes.synopsis: McKeyla and Cam question Eli at his grandmother's house and follow him to the docks, where they learn about a diabolical plan.
episodes.title: Simon Sayz

episodes.synopsis: The girls arrive at the Maywood Glen art opening to search for Vexx, but they have no idea what the elusive mastermind looks like.
episodes.title: Ear Today. Gone Tomorrow

episodes.synopsis: The girls visit NOV8's amazing headquarters, where the Quail gives them a new mission involving an old friend. But something strange is afoot.
episodes.title: A Royal Pain

episodes.synopsis: The girls try to stop an intruder from stealing a prototype from Space Inc. When things go awry, McKeyla begins to doubt her sleuthing skills.
episodes.title: If You Fail on Mars Can Anyone Hear You Scream

episodes.synopsis: McKeyla, Bryden and Adrienne discover a dark side to the nanotechnology prototype. Cam and Ember make a brainy new friend at Destination Mars Camp.
episodes.title: Nanobots, Souffles and Gray Goo, Oh My

episodes.synopsis: McKeyla homes in on a surprising new suspect: Camryn's dad! Meanwhile, Ember and Cam wonder if fellow camper Gordon is up to something.
episodes.title: Bad Air Day

episodes.synopsis: Devon uses art to help Bryden and Adrienne work through their differences. McKeyla has a difficult talk with Kyle about their relationship.
episodes.title: Totally Marble Nailed It

episodes.synopsis: The girls finally learn who's responsible for stealing the prototype. But is it too late to stop the evil mastermind's plot?
episodes.title: Gray Goo on the Loose

episodes.synopsis: The girls act fast and use their skills to name a suspect when someone threatens to sabotage a state-of-the-art urban development.
episodes.title: Stone Acres Is the Place to Be

episodes.synopsis: A new theory emerges as the girls turn their attention to the school dance -- and having dinner at Bobby Stone's cutting-edge "smart" home.
episodes.title: Smoke Gets in Your Eyes

episodes.synopsis: A familiar face from McKeyla's past steps up to help as her family connections to the case grow clearer. And "Bry-ence"? Well, it's bigger than ever.
episodes.title: Zorro Dark Thirty

episodes.synopsis: While the girls dig for more information on Bobby Stone, Adrienne and Ember make a surprising discovery about Stone Water -- and where it comes from.
episodes.title: Water from a Bobby Stone

episodes.synopsis: The girls suit up to make a scene at the Stone Water-sponsored Young Voices Awards, where McKeyla and Kyle finally talk face to face.
episodes.title: Family Affair
